          h2.mb-0 scope v2
          div should be #[span.text-success green] when scoping
    +nbr(2)
    h3 Library Scoping
    p loading external libraries ( pure css, materialize css, etc ) and apply in different parts of the same DOM tree.
    .d-flex.align-items-center
      .flex-grow-1.card.mr-4: .card-body(ld="csslib",data-name="0")
